did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.unittitle: Railway Labor Executives' Association Additional Records, 1968-1975
did.repository: Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: Files of the Railway Labor Executives' Association for the years 1968-1972.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Files of the Railway Labor Executives' Association for the years 1968-1972. General office files are included.
